<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<CONTENT id="_3793150_1"><TITLE value="Session 10"/><TITLECOLOR value="#000000"/><DESCRIPTION
   value=""/><BODY><TEXT>&lt;h4&gt;&lt;img src="@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav/xid-46884689_1" alt="" width="311" height="311" style="border: 0px solid #000000;"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;h4&gt;Introduction&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;div&gt;During this session we will investigate the behaviour based approach to cyber security.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;This is an attempt to out-think the adversary, and anticipate as much as possible.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14pt;"&gt;News&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1. &lt;a href="https://australiancybersecuritymagazine.com.au/industry-responds-to-protective-security-policy-framework-directive/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Industry Responds to Protective Security Policy Framework Directive - Australian Cyber Security Magazine&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;2. Just to show even the experts can be scammed, &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://ia.acs.org.au/article/2025/have-i-been-pwned-creator-falls-victim-to-scam.html?ref=newsletter&amp;amp;deliveryName=DM25705" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;'Have I Been Pwned' creator falls victim to scam | Information Age | ACS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;3. Failure of governance by Australian Super Funds, &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://ia.acs.org.au/article/2025/superannuation-attack-an--industry-wake-up-call-.html?ref=newsletter&amp;amp;deliveryName=DM25758" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Superannuation attack an ‘industry wake-up call’ | Information Age | ACS&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14pt;"&gt;Not Quite the News&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;From CISCO for your reading pleasure&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a alt="" href="@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav/xid-54040084_1" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Busting Passwordless Myths_CISCO Duo.pdf&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a alt="" href="@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav/xid-54040085_1" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Zero Trust Frameworks - CISCO Duo.pdf&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;&lt;a alt="" href="@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav/xid-54040086_1" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Duo-Cisco-Secure-Multi-Factor-Authentication-Guide-2022.pdf&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h4&gt;&amp;nbsp;Topic&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;During this session we will continue to investigate and examine means to proect an organisation's data.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;We will focus specifically on the following topics:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Three dimensions of security&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;IT Security Management Framework - ITSM (New topic)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Behavioural Approaches&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;CIA Triad&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;States of Data&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h5&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Out of Session Activity&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;div&gt;Review the various frameworks and approaches presented, including&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;NIST&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;McCumber cube&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;ISO Cyber Security model&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h5&gt;Portfolio Tasks&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;div&gt;Check assessments tab.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Complete outstanding work&lt;/div&gt;</TEXT><TYPE
